    {
      "question": "What payment methods do you accept?",
      "answer": "We accept all major credit cards (Visa, Mastercard, American Express) and bank transfers for annual plans. Enterprise customers can arrange custom payment terms including invoicing."
    },
    {
      "question": "Is there a free trial?",
      "answer": "Yes! All paid plans come with a 14-day free trial. No credit card required to start. You'll have full access to all features during the trial period."
    },
    {
      "question": "Do you offer discounts for nonprofits or education?",
      "answer": "Yes, we offer a 20% discount for registered nonprofits and educational institutions. Contact our sales team with your organization details to apply for the discount."
    },
    {
      "question": "What's included in support?",
      "answer": "Starter plans include email support with 24-hour response time. Professional plans get priority email and chat support with 4-hour response. Enterprise customers receive email, chat, and phone support with 1-hour SLA, plus a dedicated account manager."
    },
    {
      "question": "Can I get a refund if I'm not satisfied?",
      "answer": "Yes, we offer a 30-day money-back guarantee on all annual plans. If you're not satisfied within the first 30 days, we'll provide a full refund, no questions asked."
    },
    {
      "question": "What happens to my data if I cancel?",
      "answer": "You can export all your data at any time. After cancellation, your data is retained for 30 days, giving you time to export it. After 30 days, all data is permanently deleted according to our data retention policy."
    },
